description: Newcomer Nick was hired to strip at a Masquerade. Wanting to impress his new employer, he decided to practice before the big event. Slowly but surely he got in the mood and even excited himself as he was dancing. At the end of his number, hard as a rock, he put down his headphones and finished himself off... Lucky are those who will attend that party.
title: New Stripper At The Masquerade, Scene #01
